---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Financial Management"
  description="Get expert financial advice tailored for UK veterans, including budgeting tips, pension planning, and information on tax benefits available through the Armed Forces Compensation Scheme.">
  <div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 mb-4">Financial Management for Veterans</h1>
    <div class="row g-4">
      <div class="col-lg-8">
        <p class="lead">Managing your finances effectively is crucial for a successful transition to civilian life and long-term financial security. The Armed Forces Compensation Scheme (AFCS) offers various resources and advice to help veterans make informed financial decisions.</p>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Budgeting Advice</h2>
        <p>Learning to budget effectively can help you make the most of your compensation and income. We offer:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Personalised budgeting consultations</li>
          <li>Workshops on creating and maintaining a budget</li>
          <li>Tools and resources for tracking expenses</li>
          <li>Advice on managing debt and saving</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Pension Planning</h2>
        <p>Understanding your pension options is essential for long-term financial security. Our pension planning services include:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Information on Armed Forces Pension Schemes</li>
          <li>Guidance on civilian pension options</li>
          <li>Advice on pension transfers and consolidation</li>
          <li>Retirement planning workshops</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Tax Benefits</h2>
        <p>As a veteran, you may be eligible for various tax benefits. We provide information on:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Tax-free status of AFCS lump sum payments</li>
          <li>Potential tax relief on pension contributions</li>
          <li>VAT relief on certain goods and services for disabled veterans</li>
          <li>Council tax reductions for some veterans</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="h3 mt-4">Investment Strategies</h2>
        <p>For those looking to grow their wealth, we offer guidance on investment options:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Overview of investment types suitable for veterans</li>
          <li>Information on risk assessment and management</li>
          <li>Advice on diversifying your investment portfolio</li>
          <li>Seminars on long-term investment strategies</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>For more detailed information on each financial management topic, please visit the specific pages linked in the sidebar.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="card bg-light mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Quick Links</h3>
            <ul class="list-unstyled">
              <li><a href="/financial/budgeting" class="text-decoration-none">Budgeting Advice</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/pension-planning" class="text-decoration-none">Pension Planning</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/tax-benefits" class="text-decoration-none">Tax Benefits</a></li>
              <li><a href="/financial/investments" class="text-decoration-none">Investment Strategies</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card mb-4">
          <div class="card-body">
            <h3 class="h5">Financial Health Check</h3>
            <p>Book a free financial health check with one of our advisors to get personalised guidance on managing your finances.</p>
            <a href="/financial-health-check" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
